Take the
EF Challenge

   Record a speech on global issues and earn a ticket to New York.
   Register Upload your video

About the EF Challenge

   The EF Challenge is a high school speech competition offering students
   from around the globe the chance to win a dream trip to New York.

   Students must record a speech in response to the question:“What does
   sustainable development mean to you?”.

   The most inspiring entries will travel to the Big Apple for the EF
   Youth Leadership Forum, where they’ll debate global issues, discover
   the city and make new, lifelong friends.
   [heroImag2.jpg] [heroImag3.jpg]

Requirements

     * [language.svg]

Language
       Record your speech in English
     * [age.svg]

Age
       Students between 15 and 18 years old can participate
     * [length.svg]

Length
       Between 2 and 3 minutes is perfect
     * [upload.svg]

Upload
       Record, upload to YouTube and share it with us!

   Download here the guidelines [DownloadIcon.svg]

Prizes

     * Student Prizes
     * Teacher Prizes

Student Prizes

   Our student winners will earn an unforgettable trip to New York, where
   they’ll participate at the EF Youth Leadership Forum! The Forum brings
   together outstanding students from around the world to kick-start their
   future as potential global leaders. They’ll spend one week discussing
   big issues and exploring the Big Apple from our leafy EF Campus.

Teacher Prizes

   Our student winners will earn an unforgettable trip to New York, where
   they’ll participate at the EF Youth Leadership Forum! The Forum brings
   together outstanding students from around the world to kick-start their
   future as potential global leaders. They’ll spend one week discussing
   big issues and exploring the Big Apple from our leafy EF Campus.

Timeline

     * 1

Registration deadline
       Sign-up by April 15,2019
     * 2

Submission deadline
       Submit your speech by May 1, 2019
     * 3

Winner announcement
       The winner will be announced in your country on May 17, 2019
     * 4

Trip to New York
       The global winners travel to the EF Youth Leadership Forum on
       August XX, 2019

